<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM11.3.1">
<l>maṉṉilaṅku pāratattut tērūrntu māvaliyaip</l>
<l>poṉṉilaṅku tiṇvilaṅkil vaittup porukaṭalcūḻ</l>
<l>teṉṉilaṅkai yīṭaḻitta tēvark kitukāṇīr</l>
<l>eṉṉilaṅku caṅkō ṭeḻiltōṟ ṟiruntēṉē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>I have lost my glistening bangles and complexion - look at this -</l>
<l>To the god who destroyed the fame of Laṅkā to the South,</l>
<l rend="indent">encircled by the crashing sea,</l>
<l>Having placed Māvali in strong, glistening shackles of gold,</l>
<l>[And] having driven a chariot in the Bhārata War where warriors glistened.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
